Privacy Policy
Last Updated: January 19th 2024
This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use any application ("App") provided by Digital Edge Creations LLC ("Company").
1. Information We Collect
We collect various types of information, including but not limited to:
Personal identifiers like your name, email address, and phone number.
Usage data, such as your interactions with the App.
Device information and analytics.
2. How We Use Your Information
Your information is used for purposes such as:
Providing and improving the App.
Communicating with you about updates or offers.
Enhancing user experience and customer support.
3. Sharing Your Information
We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information with third-party providers for services such as data analysis and marketing assistance.
4. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure.
5. Compliance with GDPR
For users in the European Union, we comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). You have the right to access, correct, delete, or transfer your data. Please contact us for any such requests.
6. Compliance with Other Laws
We comply with other applicable laws and regulations related to privacy and data protection.
7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes to our practices. If we make significant changes, we will notify you through the App or via email.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at contact@digitaledgecreations.com.
By using our Apps, you consent to this Privacy Policy.